153
00:15:34,548 --> 00:15:36,120
Yeah, I'm sure we will.

154
00:15:37,483 --> 00:15:41,522
God damn, wish my daddy was a doctor then
he could have bought me a captains job.

155
00:15:41,634 --> 00:15:42,988
